		==> if equipping anything from the field is too powerful after all, a stylish way to nerf it would be only equipping monsters in the same or an adjacent column (see Scareclaws for wording) - limiting the range of the magnets
		===> wording is quite tricky (if we follow the Scareclaw precedent and only take adjacent, not adjacent column) - double "to it"!
