		{{Special Summon Level 4 "Bohrok" monster from hand or GY}}
		{{Declare 1 card name}}
		
		Regular Ja stopped effects of everything currently visible during the next turn - this one is more targeted (because it "tracks"), but takes effect immediately and can also stop threats that are not currently visible (by "sniffing them out")
		=> v4.3.2: Detaching for bonus effect cost is kinda confusing and annoying, so to fix that and bring this more in line with base Ja it's now been nerfed to protection rather than a lingering floodgate - more healthy anyway
		
